						<summary>

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Chāgi Pōtarāja</hi> made a gift of wet land to god Svayambhunātha-Mahādēva of <hi rend="bold">Kuṟukkūru.</hi> Also gives a long list of similar gifts of land made to the same temple by several other persons from time to time.</p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

						</summary>
